com.sylconnexity.spring18.util

Class RandomGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sylconnexity.spring18.util.RandomGenerator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClickGenerator, LinkGenerator, MerchantGenerator, PublisherGenerator

    public class RandomGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that randomly generates primitives such as longs and doubles. It can also generate formatted strings such as IP addresses.
